<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hiltpolt von Mendorf, Pfleger zu Hohenstein</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Peter Haidnaber, Diener der Stadt, wegen von Bayreuth nach Hohenstein verbrachter Geschirre an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_221" id="109v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_221_r1l1">Hılpolten Menndorffer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_221_r1l2"><expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒum hohenſtein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_221_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her pfleger / vns iſt <expan>fürkume<ex>n</ex></expan> . vvıe etliche </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_221_r1l4">geſchyrre <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> auf der ſtraſſe herauſʒ für </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_221_r1l5">Beyrrewrte gangen vnd cʒu euch cʒum <expan>hoh<ex>e</ex>nſtein</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_221_r1l6"><expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein / Darümb ſenden vvir cʒu euch Peter </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_221_r1l7">heydnaber <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener mit euch dauon cʒereden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_221_r1l8">vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc vt in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Do<ex>min</ex>ica</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>E<ex>pi</ex>phy<ex>a</ex><hi rend="sup">nie</hi></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_221" id="109v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hilpolten Menndorffer, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> czum Hohenstein</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her pfleger, uns ist
                            <expan>fürkume<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie etliche geschyrre
                                <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> auf der strasse herausz für
                        Beyrrewrte gangen und czu euch czum <expan>Hoh<ex>e</ex>nstein</expan>
<expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> sein. Darümb senden wir czu euch Peter
                        Heydnaber, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, mit euch davon czereden.
                        Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, etc. ut in
                            <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>e<ex>pi</ex>phy<ex>a</ex><hi rend="sup">nie</hi></expan>.</ab>
</div>
